Good morning, colleagues. I'll briefly summarize my work from yesterday and my plan for today.
- [ɡʊd ˈmɔːrnɪŋ ˈkɒliːgz aɪl ˈbriːfli ˈsʌməraɪz maɪ wɜːrk frəm ˈjestədeɪ ənd maɪ plæn fər təˈdeɪ]
- 连读：morning colleagues [ˈmɔːrnɪŋ ˈkɒliːgz]，briefly summarize [ˈbriːfli ˈsʌməraɪz]，from yesterday [frəm ˈjestədeɪ] 

Yesterday, I essentially completed the self-test for the facility rating feature. During the process, I identified some discrepancies with the design document.
- [ˈjestədeɪ aɪ ɪˈsenʃəli kəmˈpliːtɪd ðə self test fɔːr ðə fəˈsɪlɪti ˈreɪtɪŋ ˈfiːtʃəːˌdjʊərɪŋ ðə ˈprəʊses aɪ aɪˈdentɪfaɪd səm dɪsˈkrepənsiz wɪð ðə dɪˈzaɪn ˈdɒkjʊmənt]
- 连读：essentially completed [ɪˈsenʃəli kəmˈpliːtɪd]，self-test for [self test fɔːr]，discrepancies with [dɪsˈkrepənsiz wɪð] 

After communicating with the team members responsible for liaison, these issues have now been properly resolved.
- [ˈɑːftəˌ kəˈmjuːnɪkeɪtɪŋ wɪθ ðə tiːm ˈmembərz rɪˈspɒnsəbl fɔːr liˈeɪzn̩, ðiːz ˈiːʃuz hæv naʊ biːn ˈprɒpərli rɪˈzɒlvd]
- 连读：After communicating [ˈɑːftərkəˈmjuːnɪkeɪtɪŋ]，team members [tiːm ˈmembərz]，have now been [hæv naʊ biːn]

This morning, I'll continue finalizing the facility rating feature. There's just one new page left to finish, which will display reviews for all the facilities in a comprehensive list.
- [ðɪs ˈmɔːrnɪŋ, aɪl kənˈtɪnjuː ˈfaɪnəˌlaɪzɪŋ ðə fəˈsɪlɪti ˈreɪtɪŋ ˈfiːtʃəː ðerz ʤʌst wʌn njuː peɪdʒ left tə ˈfɪnɪʃ, wɪʧ wɪl dɪsˈpleɪ ˈriːvjuːz fɔːr ɔːl ðə fəˈsɪlɪtiz ɪn ə kəmˈpriːhensɪv lɪst]
- 连读：I'll continue [aɪlkənˈtɪnjuː]，facility rating [fəˈsɪlɪti ˈreɪtɪŋ]， comprehensive list [kəmˈpriːhensɪv lɪst]

Since it's a repetitive function, I've saved it for last.
- [sɪns ɪts ə rɪˈpetətɪv ˈfʌŋkʃən, aɪv seɪvd ɪt fɔː ˈlɑːst]
- 连读：it's a [ɪtsə]，I've saved [aɪvseɪvd]

In the afternoon, I plan to start on the newsfeed refactoring task. So far, it's 50% complete. It's been prioritized after the facility rating due to its lower urgency.
- [ɪn ði ˈɑːftəˌnuːn, aɪ plæn tə ˈstɑːrt ɒn ðə ˈnjuːzˌfiːd riˈfæktərɪŋ tɑːsk, soʊ fɑːr, ɪts ˈfɪfti pəˈsent kəmˈpliːt. ɪts biːn praɪˈɒrɪˌtaɪzd ˈɑːftə ðə fəˈsɪlɪti ˈreɪtɪŋ djuː tə ɪts ˈləʊər ˈɜːdʒənsi]
- 连读：in the afternoon [ɪn ðiˈɑːftənuːn]，to start on [təˈstɑːrton]，50% complete [ˈfɪftipəˈsentkəmˈpliːt]

If any of you have questions or suggestions, please feel free to let me know.
- [ɪf ˈɛni əv ju: hæv ˈkwesʧənz ɔːr səˈdʒesʧənz, pli:z fi:l fri: tə ˈlet mi ˈnoʊ]
- 连读：please feel free [pli:z fi:l fri:]， let me know [letminou]

That's all from my side.
- [ðæts ɔːl frəm maɪ saɪd]
- 注释：这句较短且没有明显的连读现象。
  
连读的地方被表示为紧凑在一起的单词。注意，连读并不意味着两个词中间没有间隙，而是指的音节的自然过渡，尤其是辅音和元音相连的地方。弱读常出现在语气词（如助词、介词等）上，使得主要内容词可以更加突出。在练习发音时，记得模仿这些连读和弱读，以便提高你的口语流畅性和自然度。